  "body": "In `NewStateRecalculations` from `crystallized_state.go` Every block, we are suppose to compare the attester's participated balance to the total balance of the block if every attester has participated. \r\n\r\nThere's a bug of the current code where attester's participated balance is compared with the total deposits of the crystallized state. This is incorrect we should compare to the total deposits of the attester in that slot committee. ",
