    "body": "Confirmed with Danny, the spec is a lil confusing but it's actually correct.\r\n\r\nWhen a validator attest to a block. It actually is attesting up to CYCLE_LENGTH blocks. For each block, after a full cycle, there is a chance for every validator to have attested to it and we are counting block votes from the direct block attested to but all the other slots that get attested to implicitly although explicitly signed.",
